I’m reminiscing and putting these past three years of my life away. Giving myself completely freedom and thanking god for being with me the whole way. How much I have mentally change in the past year. Maybe because im getting older? How I look back and wonder, how did I survive. How did i do that? Divorce, lost my mom moved five times. It sounds crazy but when you are at your highest in life you are also at your lowest. I’ll be honest I wasn’t sober neither I was a alcoholic. I numb all my feeling that I needed to actually feel. I will tell you it definitely sucks being sober but once you figure out what you are able to do without it. Great things in life come. I want to thank god for healing me and allowing me to give myself freedom to let it go and move on because you are capable of forgiveness in yourself and other people and become the best version of yourself. I’m so excited to be there for MIAMI SWIM WEEK!
